  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p><span id="accommodation_info">Each morning the staff prepare the breakfast buffet with a wide selection of fresh fruits, breads, pastries and cereals. There are also Sicilian specialties like granita and brioche. </span><span id="accommodation_info">If you choose half board you'll get a four-course dinner with choices in the Pirandello Restaurant. In the summer there's a weekly buffet Sicilian evening accompanied by live music. </span></p>
<p><span id="accommodation_info"><strong>Pirandello Restaurant </strong>is in the main hotel and serves an à la carte menu of traditional Sicilian and international dishes. In the summer dine outside on the panoramic terrace. </span></p>
<p><strong>La Terrazza Restaurant </strong>opens during the summer and you can enjoy candlelit dinners on the hotel's spectacular sky terrace. The terrace restaurant serves delicious grilled dishes including fresh local fish. </p>
<p><span><strong>The Grill Restaurant</strong> is located on the terrace. Enjoy al fresco lunches here in the summer months.</span></p>
<p><strong>The Main Bar </strong>is a traditional bar serving  aselection of drinks including aperitivo and cocktails.</p>
<p><strong>Poolside Bar </strong>serves drinks, snacks and ice cream that you can have while relaxing beside the pool.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
