  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard</strong> <strong>Balcony Rooms</strong> are about 16-24m² and are decorated in a fresh Mediterranean style. They sleep up to three people and have a balcony, air conditioning (high season), TV, minibar, tea &amp; coffee making facilities, safe and bath or shower. Cots are available free of charge. </p>
<p><strong>Standard Sea View Rooms </strong>are about 16-24m² with views across the Ionian Sea. They can sleep up to three people and have bathrobes and slippers.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> are about 22m² with a furnished balcony with views across the Ionian Sea. They sleep up to three people and come with free soft drinks in the minibar, deluxe toiletries, bathrobes, slippers and a turn down service.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
